DEPENDENCIES
------------

+ Debian packages:

# apt-get install <package>

	+ perl
	+ perl-modules
	+ sudo
	+ liblog-dispatch-perl
	+ liblog-log4perl-perl
	+ liblocale-gettext-perl
	+ libnet-ip-perl
	+ liberror-perl
	+ libdevel-stacktrace-perl
	+ libhtml-mason-perl
	+ gettext
        + libfile-slurp-perl

+ modules from CPAN

	+ Perl6::Junction
        + Readonly
        + Readonly::XS (recommended)

INSTALATION
-----------

1.- Configure:

    $ ./configure <arguments>

    Accepts standard GNU configure arguments, run ./configure --help
    for a list

    Suggested argument: --localstatedir=/var/ , to have variable data
    installed in /var/lib/, instead of the default $prefix/var/lib/

2.- Installation, as root:

    $ make install
